VDD vdcbias GND {VDS}
LDD d vdcbias 1u m=1
COUT d out 10p m=1
CIN in s 10p m=1
V1 in GND DC 0 AC 1 0 portnum 1 z0 50
V2 out GND DC 0 AC 1 0 portnum 2 z0 50
LSRC GND s 10u m=1
